// Mask-coverage fixture — exercises the self-only mask shape landed by
// task 141. Hold / MoveToward / Flee are all permissive for alive
// agents; real gates live in scoring. The task 141 commit deletes the
// matching hand-written `mark_*_allowed` bodies in
// `crates/engine/src/mask.rs` in favour of these predicates.
mask Hold       when agents.alive(self)
mask MoveToward when agents.alive(self)
mask Flee       when agents.alive(self)
